snippet.title: Door Kickers 2 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist/follow on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1239080/Door_Kickers_2_Task_Force_North/

Command military Special Ops Teams in gripping tactical combat against a Middle East-based terrorist network. Sequel to RockPaperShotgun's "Best Tactics Game of 2014".
Early Access coming circa Q2 2020.

https://discord.gg/doorkickers
https://inthekillhouse.com/doorkickers2
https://www.facebook.com/KillHouseGames/
